      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-07-29T12:37:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Bigger question: Do tiles matter anymore? If the goal of tiles is to make it easy to identify which params exist in a segment of data, I think you can now do that with a JOIN to TraceValues query.\n\nSELECT DISTINCT TraceNames.params from\n  TraceNames\nJOIN\n  TraceValues2\nON TraceNames.trace_id \u003d TraceValues2.trace_id\nWHERE TraceValues2.commit_number \u003e 500 AND TraceValues2.commit_number \u003c 1000;",
      "range": {
